      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pad Thai sauce</strong> to the pan[s] with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and<strong> chopped spring onion </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cooked noodles</strong></p><p>Cook for a final 1 min and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chicken pad Thai</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
